<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.6.3">
<l>nīrvāṉam maṇṇerikā lāyniṉṟa neṭumāltaṉ</l>
<l>tārāya naṟuntuḷavam perantakaiyeṟ karuḷāṉē</l>
<l>cīrārum vaḷarppoḻilcūḻ tiruvāli vayalvāḻum</l>
<l>kūrvāya ciṟukurukē. kuṟippaṟintu kūṟāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tall Māl, who endures as water, sky, earth, fire, [and] wind,</l>
<l rend="indent">is not gracious to me</l>
<l>Who is worthy of receiving the fragrant tulasī which has become his garland;</l>
<l>Little sharp-beaked heron who dwells in the paddy fields of sacred Āli</l>
<l>Encircled by excellent, tall groves, having fathomed [his] purpose, tell [me].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
